::Prowl/Striker::

An thrill runs through Prowl's spine as Iron Raptor puts her arm around him, 
reminding him of how he held her in her quarters only a short time ago. His 
hands slide to her back as as she puts her head on his shoulder, clearing the 
thought of the battle or of damage totaly from his mind as he felt her 
against him. He nods as he hears her speak, the vibrations sending an 
exciting feeling up his spine.

"All right," he says, his breath speeding up as she strokes his neck. 
Whatever he was about to add was forgotten as she quickly kisses him, walking 
off toward Plintissa.

He follows her, his eyes glued to her body as she moves toward Plintissa. He 
walks up to her as Plintissa and Dracona do, and puts an arm around her 
waist, pressing her to him. He growls silently as he hears the sound of shots 
followed by an avalance outside.

"I'll go see what's up," he says, kissing Iron Raptor, reluctantly letting go 
of her, and walking off toward the exit of the Ark, his hand on his gun just 
in case.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Striker walks out of the CR chamber, recieving Bronko's transmission. He 
curses under his breath, sending a comm to Iron Raptor.

"A bot has just sent a transmission that requires your attention," he says 
into his comm-link, walking off toward the bridge,
